Veepdotai is a project to create a complete autonomous virtual presence through voice, from web site to LinkedIn page and, at the end, each social network. A true #nosouci solution :-)

== Description ==

The Veep project aims at providing thanks to voice recognition a solution to create an autonomous online presence composed of:
* one web site, autonomous
* one LinkedIn profile, autonomous

Autonomous means content is created each day, week, month by the AI for the website, then declined in posts (with carroussel) for LinkedIn, while the LinkedIn audience is augmented through automatic connections each week.

== Installation ==

This section describes how to install the plugin and get it working.

e.g.

1. Upload `veepdotai.zip` to the `/wp-content/plugins/` directory
1. Activate the plugin through the 'Plugins' menu in WordPress
1. Place `<?php do_action('plugin_name_hook'); ?>` in your templates

